<h2>Welcome to Best Small Country</h2>

<p>
This could be <em>your</em> story.
Discrimination <em>IS</em> legal in Ireland.
Ireland believes it's a fair and inclusive society.

Unless you're fortunate enough to belong to one of
<a href="https://www.ihrec.ie/your-rights/i-have-an-issue-with-a-service/what-categories-of-people-are-covered-by-the-law-on-discrimination-in-relation-to-services/">
nine groups</a>, delusional Ireland offers you <em>NO PROTECTION</em>.
</p>

